Module org.example.camping2
Package org.example.camping2.dto

Class Recurso

java.lang.Object
org.example.camping2.dto.Recurso
@Entity public class Recurso extends Object
Entity representing a resource in the camping system. This class holds information about a resource, such as its name, type, capacity, price, minimum number of people, and status. The entity is mapped to the `recurso` table in the database.
Since:
31/01/2025
Version:
1.0.0
Author:
Andrews Dos Ramos
